====Usage notes====
''Frei'' can mean “free of charge” only in the context of public services, e.g. ''freie Krankenversorgung'' ("free medical care"), and in some fixed expressions such as {{m|de|Freibier||free beer}} or {{m|de|freie Kost und Logis||free board and lodge}}. Otherwise, ''frei'' is not applicable in this sense. Instead, {{m|de|kostenlos}} should be used.

